      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Forest_Hills%2C_Queens"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "From 1915 to 1978, Forest Hills hosted the Open Tennis Championships, and legends like the Beatles and Bob Dylan performed there.",
